OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774455107
OL,3,CTeenager jailed for killing mother
OL,4,Cwith a hammer because of 'hatred of
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FA north Wales teenager has been
OL,8,Fsentenced to life imprisonment with a
OL,9,Fminimum jail term of 22 and a half
OL,10,Fyears for the murder of his mother.
OL,12,FTristan Roberts from Prestatyn
OL,13,Fappeared before Mold Crown Court on
OL,14,FWednesday 25 March after carrying out
OL,15,Fthe gruesome attack on 23 October last
OL,16,Fyear, just ten days after his 18th
OL,17,Fbirthday.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774455107
OL,3,CTeenager jailed for killing mother
OL,4,Cwith a hammer because of 'hatred of
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FThe court heard he planned Angela
OL,8,FShellis' murder for at least three
OL,9,Fweeks before he attacked her at their
OL,10,Fhome on Coniston Drive.
OL,12,FHe tricked her to leave their house to
OL,13,Fget medical help but walked her to the
OL,14,Fnearby Morfa nature reserve where he
OL,15,Fmurdered her with a hammer.
OL,17,FHe left her body to be discovered by
OL,18,Fwalkers.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
