FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774455107
OL,3,CTeenager jailed for killing mother
OL,4,Cwith a hammer because of 'hatred of
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FThe teenager who is autistic and has
OL,8,FADHD showed little emotion throughout
OL,9,Fproceedings in court. He plead guilty
OL,10,Fto the murder of his 45-year-old
OL,11,Fmother at a previous hearing.
OL,13,FThe court heard how he was fuelled by
OL,14,Fhatred for her and women and girls in
OL,15,Fgeneral. He used the online forum
OL,16,F"Discord" for several hours a day and
OL,17,Flaid out his plans to fellow users.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@IO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/17
