OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774455107
OL,3,CTeenager jailed for killing mother
OL,4,Cwith a hammer because of 'hatred of
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FMs Shellis had tried to get help for
OL,8,Fher son as she grew concerned about
OL,9,Fhis mental health. Notes she wrote
OL,10,Falso show she was worried for her own
OL,11,Fsafety and knew he was stockpiling
OL,12,Fweapons.
OL,14,FThose at Mold Crown Court heard how it
OL,15,Fwas a pre-meditated murder by Roberts
OL,16,Fwith extensive planning over a period
OL,17,Fof at least three weeks. The attack
OL,18,Flasted more than 4 hours.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
