PN,46205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774455107
OL,3,CTeenager jailed for killing mother
OL,4,Cwith a hammer because of 'hatred of
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FTo prepare for the murder he bought
OL,8,Fknives, hammers and an axe online plus
OL,9,Fa dictaphone so he could record
OL,10,Fhimself killing his mother.
OL,12,FHe had become obsessed with weapons
OL,13,Fand had been carrying a knife around
OL,14,Fin his rucksack.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
