PN,46206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774455107
OL,3,CTeenager jailed for killing mother
OL,4,Cwith a hammer because of 'hatred of
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FJust a few weeks before he murdered Ms
OL,8,FShellis, Roberts had been in court for
OL,9,Fcarrying a knife in a public place. On
OL,10,Fthe night of the attack in October he
OL,11,Fstruck his mother with a hammer and
OL,12,Fstrangled her in their own home on
OL,13,FConiston Drive, Prestatyn.
OL,15,FAngela Shellis attack and murder was
OL,16,Frecorded on the dictaphone.
OL,18,FMs Shellis pleaded with her son to
OL,19,Fcall 999.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774455107
OL,3,CTeenager jailed for killing mother
OL,4,Cwith a hammer because of 'hatred of
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FBut instead he made her put on a
OL,8,Fbalaclava to leave the house. The
OL,9,Fcourt heard he did this to minimise
OL,10,Fblood splatter when he dealt the
OL,11,Fdevastating hammer blows which killed
OL,12,Fher.
OL,14,FHe told Ms Shellis that the quickest
OL,15,Froute to get to town was through the
OL,16,Fnature reserve. They were captured on
OL,17,FCCTV and can be seen crossing the
OL,18,Frailway line. Ms Shellis is seen still
OL,19,Fwearing her slippers and walking with
OL,20,Fa crutch.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774455107
OL,3,CTeenager jailed for killing mother
OL,4,Cwith a hammer because of 'hatred of
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FWhen at the reserve, Roberts told his
OL,8,Fmother to sit down on a bench. He then
OL,9,Fproduced a heavy lump hammer.
OL,11,FShe began screaming - she can be heard
OL,12,Fon the dictaphone. She pleaded with
OL,13,Fhim not to kill her.
OL,15,FHe recorded himself saying "I just
OL,16,Fkilled her" and complaining about his
OL,17,Fdiscomfort having to move her. He
OL,18,Fdragged her body and abandoned it in
OL,19,Fundergrowth where she was found by
OL,20,Fwalkers.
OL,26,@wD@\OUxD@KO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/17
