PN,46209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774455107
OL,3,CTeenager jailed for killing mother
OL,4,Cwith a hammer because of 'hatred of
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FAt 5.30am he returned home.
OL,9,FDuring his sentencing on Wednesday,
OL,10,Fthe court heard that Tristan Roberts
OL,11,Fwaited until he was 18 to buy a knife
OL,12,Ffrom a Rhyl store. The shop assistant
OL,13,Fhad concerns and flagged the sale to
OL,14,Fher manager but because he was 18 the
OL,15,Fsale went through. The sales person
OL,16,Fwas so concerned they kept a copy of
OL,17,Fthe receipt.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
