FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774455107
OL,3,CTeenager jailed for killing mother
OL,4,Cwith a hammer because of 'hatred of
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FMs Shellis had become extremely
OL,8,Fconcerned about her son's behaviour
OL,9,Fand on 17 October 2025 she messaged
OL,10,Fsocial workers expressing concern
OL,11,Fabout his mental health.
OL,13,FShe wrote a note to herself asking "Is
OL,14,Fhe planning to hurt me?"
OL,16,FHe boasted online about what he had
OL,17,Fdone on the forum "Discord".
OL,26,@uD@dOUvD@XO]yD@SOUyD@[O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/17
