PN,46211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774455107
OL,3,CTeenager jailed for killing mother
OL,4,Cwith a hammer because of 'hatred of
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FOn the morning of 24 October the
OL,8,Fvictim's other son Ethan asked
OL,9,Frepeatedly for his mum to call him but
OL,10,Fshe didn't.
OL,12,FInstead he received messages from his
OL,13,Fbrother pretending to be her. Ethan
OL,14,Fcalled his grandparents- they went to
OL,15,Fto the house but Tristan barricaded
OL,16,Fhimself inside.
OL,18,FIn a victim impact statement, Angela's
OL,19,Feldest son Ethan said his mum was "the
OL,20,Fmost important person in my life. We
OL,21,Ftalked every day."
OL,26,@{D@cOU}D@RO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774455107
OL,3,CTeenager jailed for killing mother
OL,4,Cwith a hammer because of 'hatred of
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FHe said "all my mum ever did was love
OL,8,FTristan. He's the one who took her
OL,9,Ffrom us all."
OL,11,FAngela's sister Sarah Gunther took to
OL,12,Fthe stand to read her victim
OL,13,Fstatement. She said "Tristan , I
OL,14,Fwanted to look you in the eyes and say
OL,15,Fthis to you. As a close family we all
OL,16,Ffought so hard to get you help. None
OL,17,Fof us gave up on you. There is anger,
OL,18,Fconfusion, heartbreak but for me
OL,19,Fpersonally there is still care for
OL,20,Fyou."
OL,26,@oD@IOUqD@MO]uD@UOU|D@EO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774455107
OL,3,CTeenager jailed for killing mother
OL,4,Cwith a hammer because of 'hatred of
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FShe added "You shattered everything".
OL,9,FShe went on to say "I hope the
OL,10,Fservices that failed my sister and
OL,11,Fnephew will be held accountable".
OL,13,FHis defence team argued Roberts did
OL,14,Fnot get the mental health support he
OL,15,Fshould have but in part that was down
OL,16,Fto his failure to engage.
OL,18,FSentencing him today Judge Rhys
OL,19,FRowlands told Roberts "you clearly are
OL,20,Fa very dangerous individual who has
OL,21,Fshown little or no remorse."
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@dO]qD@TOUsD@`O]{D@WOU}D@\O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/17
