OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774455107
OL,3,CTeenager jailed for killing mother
OL,4,Cwith a hammer because of 'hatred of
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,F"You produced a hammer and you struck
OL,8,Fher a number of times to the head. It
OL,9,Fwas a truly awful way for someone to
OL,10,Fdie and the attacker was her own son.
OL,11,FSomeone she cared for and worried
OL,12,Fabout in the weeks before her death.
OL,14,F"She was vulnerable with limited
OL,15,Fmobility, having injured her knee. As
OL,16,Fof last autumn you were behaving in a
OL,17,Fdisruptive and aggressive nature.
OL,18,FIndeed A matter of months earlier you
OL,19,Fwere in court for having a knife in a
OL,20,Fpublic place.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
